Java-GLSL
===================
This project contains some simple examples with java + glsl + opengl

js.ui.blob.BlobApplication
-------------------
Example video: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=823Q4QyxyQI

js.ui.particle.ParticleApplication
-------------------
Example video: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1o4NM5IbAwg

Tested with
-------------------
- Java 6
- Maven 3
- Windows 7 64bit, AMD
- IntelliJ IDEA

Getting started
-------------------
1) Execute external/jogl-2.0-rc3/install.bat
2) Open Project in IntelliJ IDEA
3) Run main method of js.ui.blob.BlobApplication or js.ui.particle.ParticleApplication
